                <note rend="inline" type="source">714.1515/587: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geissler</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-03-21T18:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 21, 1928—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>25. The Acting Minister for Foreign Affairs says that Cuyamel would be acceptable
                    and that the Guatemalan Commissioners will meet with the others at such time and
                    place as the Department may suggest.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Tegucigalpa and Costa Rica.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Geissler</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
